  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="MTA25">
<l>uraimēṟkoṇ ṭeṉṉuḷḷa mōvā teppōtum</l>
<l>varaimēṉ marakatamē pōlat – tiraimēṟ</l>
<l>kiṭantāṉaik kīṇṭāṉaik kēḻalāyp pūmi</l>
<l>yiṭantāṉai yētti yeḻum.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Taking up words, my heart, without stopping, always</l>
<l>rises praising him who, like the emerald on the mountain,</l>
<l>rested on the waves, who tore open [Hiraṇya’s chest],</l>
<l>who dug up the earth as a boar.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
